    <body> 

        <section name="Download"> 
            <p> 
                Here you can download the latest version of Checkstyle Beans plugin.
            </p>
            <p>
                After the installation the plugin should start working immediately.
                When you open a new source file or save an existing one you should
                see the Checkstyle annotations.
            </p>

            <p>
                <strong>Choose version 3.x.x in order to use NetBeans 7/8 and Checkstyle 5.7.</strong>
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>Choose version 2.x.x in order to use Checkstyle 5.</strong>
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>Choose version 1.x.x in order to use Checkstyle 4.</strong>
            </p>
            
            <p>
                In version 3.0.0 with support for NetBeans 7 and Checkstyle 5.4
                plugin had to be incompatibly changed (as Checkstyle 5.4 itself did so).
            </p>

            <p>
                In version 2.0.0 with support for Checkstyle 5 plugin had to be
                incompatibly changed (as Checkstyle 5 itself did so).
            </p>

            <p>
                The integrated GUI builder filter was removed in version
                1.2.0. You can use this as custom filter in standard way
                since then. This filter is now part of the <a href="extra.html">Extra Code</a>.
            </p>         
        </section>

